message: The Resourcelink is a copyright violation. Please read the terms of Gartner. The list of vendors is one-sided and misleading advertising. Wikipedia is an independent site. Why the list is not listed in alphabetical form?!? :)
@billinghurst: i have added the language code.
i don´t have a conflict of interest. i want only that you list ALL of MDM companies or NONE. Do not advertise here!
Please don´t vandalise. do you work for one of this four companies?

Extract from Gartner MDM 2012,G00230508 Page 23: A leading vendor is not a default choice for all buyers, and clients are warned not to assume that they should buy only from the Leaders quadrant. The Resourcelink is a copyright violation. Contact Gartner!
I think  it´s really unfair that  one lists the leading companies without mentioning smaller companies.. If you list companies, you should list every company or none. It distorts competition.
